## Dataset Used

### Iris Dataset

The Iris dataset contains:

* 150 samples
* 3 flower classes
* 4 features

### Flower Classes

* Setosa
* Versicolor
* Virginica

### Features

* Sepal Length
* Sepal Width
* Petal Length
* Petal Width

